data.description: This customized version of the Melody floorplan boasts upgrades including 10-foot ceilings, 9-foot doors, extended cabinetry, quartz countertops throughout, coffee bar, open entryway, expansive island, and Cat5 ethernet ports in all rooms. Not to mention the standard features that come with a Vierra builders' home: access to Addison Village Club (pool, gym, tennis courts, etc.), Extended 10-year warranty, lawn & landscaping included, excellent schools, and an extremely safe and family-friendly neighborhood. Some photos are virtually staged.
